pageContext.claim: “You know outside, I don't know what this place holds, like, 10,000 - 11,000 people, right? Outside you have thousands and thousands of people that want to get in.  There's never been a movement like this.”
pageContext.analysis: The arena was packed, but it holds just 8,000 people.Some people watched on a monitor outside but photos do not suggest it was "thousands and thousands."
